      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im 5 months pregnant and i have such a bad sinus infection. my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i have some pseudoephedrine (sudafed) left over from before i was pregnant, can i just take a couple of those to help clear my nose? i really need some relief so i can sleep",
