      "content": "Take a couple of those Sudafed tablets, but make sure to follow the dosage instructions on the package. If you're really struggling, you can also try a few drops of essential oils like eucalyptus or peppermint in a diffuser. Remember, it's always best to consult with your healthcare provider before taking any medication during pregnancy, but these options might give you some temporary relief. Good luck and rest well!",
      "source": "target",
